snippet.title: OVERWATCH 2: INVASION TRAILER | STORY MISSIONS, NEW SUPPORT HERO & MORE
snippet.description:
Introducing Overwatch 2: Invasion, an all-new adventure and the biggest content drop to date! Immerse yourself in the highly anticipated Story Missions, play as a new Support hero, hone your skills with Hero Mastery Missions, take aim at the Firing Range, and group up with friends in an all new Co-op experience. 

New maps, new missions, and all-new ways to play await in Overwatch 2: Invasion, coming August 10.
_
